## Your Task

Design the cast for this novel. Aim for 4-6 characters total — a tight cast, not a sprawling one. Include 1-2 POV characters, 1-2 antagonists, and 2-3 supporting characters.

IMPORTANT: Keep each character's entry concise. Biographies should be 2 sentences. Speaking traits should be a few keywords. Do not write paragraphs where a phrase will do.

For each character, provide these fields as JSON:
- name, aliases (array), age
- biography (2 sentences max)
- motives: {primary: str, secondary: str}
- fears (array of short strings)
- desires (array of short strings)
- secrets (array, at least one)
- social_position (one phrase)
- speaking_traits: {pattern: str, vocabulary: str}
- movement_traits: {posture: str, gesture: str}
- moral_constraints (array)
- arc_hypothesis (one sentence)
- is_pov_character (true/false)
- relationships: [{character: str, type: str, description: str}]

Also provide relationship_dynamics: one paragraph on how the cast creates tension.

Respond with a JSON object matching the CastResponse schema.
